1 NOTE Bio notes: James John Stanton was born in 1845. He married Mary Cosgrove in 1857 in Aghada, Cork, Ireland. They had 14 children in 23 years. He moved around a lot. He was born in Mayo, Ireland, and got married there too. He later lived in Manchester, Lancashire, England, in 1961. Then, he moved back to Ireland to have three of his children in Ireland. In 1871, he was recorded living in Govan, Lanarksshire, Scotland. Came back to Shanandoah in 1874 and owned a piece of land  in Shenandoah; Mahanoy, Schuylkill, PA. He died on December 27, 1891, in Shenandoah, PA, when he was 46 years old.
